<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们没有再去火车站，但是他们经常去铁路边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很快就认识了所有经过的火车，还给它们起了名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>9点15分的是“绿龙”，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>10点7分的是“温切斯特虫”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，他们坐在山坡上等绿龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绿龙去伦敦。”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果它是一条真的龙，我们可以拜托它把我们的爱带给爸爸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙不会帮人传递爱。”彼得说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们太凶猛了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你能驯服它们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59825</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们就能像狗一样叼东西。”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们还能从你手上拿东西吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对了，爸爸怎么从来不给我们写信？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈说他很忙。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是她说爸爸很快就会给我们写信了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绿龙经过的时候，我们一起向它挥手吧。”菲利斯提议说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它会把我们的爱带给爸爸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们对火车挥动着手帕……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车上也有人对他们挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那只手上拿着报纸，是一位老先生的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是一位英俊的老人，头发白白的，带着一顶礼帽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们每天都向他挥手，他也挥手回应。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这段时间，妈妈一直忙着写作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她寄出许多装着故事的信封，也收到许多信封。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候，她打开信封说：“哦，怎么办！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们就会觉得很可惜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是有时候，妈妈会挥动着信封说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杂志社买下了我的故事！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后就会买面包当茶点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，彼得去小镇上买面包时，遇到了站长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好！”站长友好地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早……早上好！”彼得紧张地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好久没见你来火车站了。”站长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那件事以后……”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那件事已经过去了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以随时过来！”站长笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，谢谢您！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，孩子们向绿龙挥手后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得带着姐妹们去了火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们真的可以去吗？上次那件事……”菲利斯怀疑地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天我遇到了站长，他说我们随时都可以去。”彼得回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在火车站，孩子们遇到了站台工作人员帕克斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和其他的大人不同，帕克斯会耐心地回答他们的各种问题，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还告诉他们许多铁路方面的知识。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们知道以前有一个人写下了他看到的每一列火车的号码。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得觉得他也可以这么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帕克斯给了他一个信封，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得在上面写下了379和663。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天回家以后，彼得向妈妈要一个笔记本。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈递给他说：“你们喜欢铁路，我很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是不要在铁轨上走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“面对火车来的方向也不行吗？”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比说：“妈妈，你小的时候没有在铁轨上走过吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈诚实地说：“我也走过……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那这样吧，你们可以在铁轨上走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是不能去隧道里或拐角处。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>